testprocedure.test-case-summary: This test procedure is called by a test case and is used to verify the SUTs support of the dlFullEventUpdateRequest dialog as an OC using variables provided by the calling test case. This procedure supports verification of requirements related to user need 2.3.6.1.7 [Need for Event Data] and is used for both valid and invalid test cases.
